&lt;p&gt;Your &lt;code&gt;else if&lt;/code&gt; will trigger whenever the script finds a line that doesn't match the submitted username, rather than when it gets to the end of the file. You'll need to move that check outside of the loop so that the new username is only added once. Altogether, now:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code&gt;$fh = @fopen("whitelist.txt", 'a+');
